    "updated_at": "2026-03-24T12:49:02Z",
    "body": "Hi, I've been looking into this and traced the root cause.\n\n**Proposed approach:** 1. In src/modules/pixi.rs: read PIXI_PROJECT_NAME via context.get_env(\"PIXI_PROJECT_NAME\"). 2. Add \"project_name\" match arm in the .map() closure alongside the existing \"environment\" arm. 3. In src/configs/pixi.rs: optionally update default format string to include project_name, or leave as opt-in. 4. Add tests following the existing environment variable mocking pattern. 5. Update docs (docs/config/README.md or similar) to document the new placeholder.\n\nI'll open a draft PR shortly. Happy to adjust based on your preference.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
