    "updated_at": "2026-03-24T12:59:30Z",
    "body": "I'd like to take a shot at this. My approach:\n\n1. Read `PIXI_PROJECT_NAME` env var in the pixi module (same pattern as `PIXI_ENVIRONMENT_NAME`)\n2. Add `project_name` as a format variable in the string formatter\n3. Update docs to document the new variable\n4. Add unit tests for both set and unset cases\n\nWill open a draft PR shortly.",
